OL,3,CHumza Yousaf: Politician who was
OL,4,Ctipped for the top from the start of
OL,5,Chis career
OL,7,FAfter just over a year, First Minister
OL,8,FHumza Yousaf announced his resignation
OL,9,Ffollowing the collapse of the power-
OL,10,Fsharing deal between the SNP and
OL,11,FScottish Greens.
OL,13,FSpeaking at Bute House just after noon
OL,14,Fon Monday, Mr Yousaf said he made the
OL,15,Fdecision in order to "repair our
OL,16,Frelationship across the political
OL,17,Fdivide" in Scotland.
