OL,3,CHumza Yousaf: Politician who was
OL,4,Ctipped for the top from the start of
OL,5,Chis career
OL,7,F"After spending the weekend reflecting
OL,8,Fon what is best for my party, for the
OL,9,Fgovernment and for the country I lead,
OL,10,FI have concluded that repairing our
OL,11,Frelationship across the political
OL,12,Fdivide can only be done with someone
OL,13,Felse at the helm.
OL,15,F"I have therefore informed the SNP's
OL,16,Fnational secretary of my intention to
OL,17,Fstand down as party leader and ask
OL,18,Fthat she commences a leadership
OL,19,Fcontest for my replacement as soon as
OL,20,Fpossible."
