OL,7,FWhile he has avoided being the
OL,8,Fshortest incumbent of the post, a
OL,9,Ftitle held by Labour's Henry McLeish,
OL,10,Fwho was in office for one year and 12
OL,11,Fdays between 2000 and 2001, Mr Yousaf
OL,12,Fhas always had a tricky tenure.
OL,14,FHere is how he got the top job in
OL,15,FScottish politics.
OL,17,FWhere did Hamza Yousaf start his
OL,18,Fcareer?
