OL,3,CHumza Yousaf: Politician who was
OL,4,Ctipped for the top from the start of
OL,5,Chis career
OL,7,FHamza Yousaf began in 2009 as a
OL,8,Fpolitical staffer, first working for
OL,9,FBashir Ahmad ` the country's first
OL,10,FMuslim MSP ` and then-First Minister
OL,11,FAlex Salmond and his deputy Nicola
OL,12,FSturgeon.
OL,14,FIn 2011, Mr Yousaf was one of the new
OL,15,Fnationalist MSPs who swept to Holyrood
OL,16,Fin the first majority the Scottish
OL,17,FParliament had seen.
