OL,4,Ctipped for the top from the start of
OL,5,Chis career
OL,7,FWhat followed was a 12-year journey
OL,8,Fthrough various ministerial offices
OL,9,Fand some of the toughest posts in the
OL,10,FScottish Government, before he claimed
OL,11,Fthe top job.
OL,13,FHis early life
OL,15,FBorn in Glasgow in 1985 to Muzaffar
OL,16,FYousaf and Shaaista Bhutta, a life in
OL,17,Fpolitics was not his parents' first
OL,18,Fhope for their son.
