OL,7,FMr Yousaf has spoken repeatedly about
OL,8,Fhow his family hoped he would become a
OL,9,Fdoctor or a lawyer, but instead he
OL,10,Fchose to study politics at Glasgow
OL,11,FUniversity, joining the SNP in 2005.
OL,13,FIn his early life, he crossed paths
OL,14,Fwith future Scottish Labour leader
OL,15,FAnas Sarwar, who is two years his
OL,16,Fsenior and also attended the private
OL,17,FHutcheson's Grammar on Glasgow's south
OL,18,Fside.
