OL,7,FHe has joked that he has Mr Sarwar's
OL,8,Ffather, the UK's first Muslim MP
OL,9,FMohammed Sarwar, on speed dial should
OL,10,Finteractions between the two in the
OL,11,Fchamber become too heated.
OL,13,FFirst years in parliament
OL,15,FElected on the Glasgow list in 2011,
OL,16,FMr Yousaf spent his first year in
OL,17,Fparliament on the backbenches, before
OL,18,Fbeing tipped for ministerial office by
OL,19,FMr Salmond following a year as
OL,20,Fparliamentary aide to the then-first
OL,21,Fminister.
